source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_00<tab>Midnight Dew is too busy to fill all her orders on her own.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_00<tab>Midnight Dew cherche une personne à qui confier une petite livraison.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_01<tab>Midnight Dew has received an order for a bag of squigglywogs, but she's simply too busy to deliver it. She asks you to take it to Feltsmox, who should be fishing, as usual, at the Thaliak River.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_01<tab>Midnight Dew vous a demandé de livrer un article à Feltsmox. Trouvez la Gobeline au bord de la rivière Thaliak et remettez-lui <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B1E0202 /var> qu'elle a commandé.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_02<tab>Feltsmox thanks you for the squigglywogs. She has been having terrible luck fishing lately, but these wriggly little tadpoles make such exceptional bait that her luck should start to turn immediately. She gives you a bag of coins in payment─take it back to Midnight Dew.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_02<tab>Feltsmox vous a remis <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B1F0202 /var> et vous a remercié<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>. Rapportez l'argent à Midnight Dew à Idyllée.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_03<tab>You return Feltsmox's payment to Midnight Dew. She explains that fishing is a popular pastime amongst goblins, and the resulting demand for squigglywogs is helping her turn a tidy profit. While the goblins plan to settle a town in Idyllshire, Midnight Dew suspects that many goblins are just natural-born wanderers. She doubts it will be long before Feltsmox feels the need to leave the city and travel the realm.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_SEQ_03<tab>D'après Midnight Dew, si beaucoup de Gobelins veulent s'installer à Idyllée, leur peuple est à l'origine nomade. Elle pense que Feltsmox n'a pas perdu ses habitudes de vagabonde, et quittera peut-être un jour cette nouvelle vie sédentaire.
TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_TODO_00<tab>Livrer <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B1E0202 /var> à Feltsmox, près de la rivière Thaliak

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_TODO_01<tab>Deliver Feltsmox's payment to Midnight Dew.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_TODO_01<tab>Remettre <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B1F0202 /var> à Midnight Dew à Idyllée

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_050<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Not one fishbite all day! What trick can Feltsmox use to catch more fish...?
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_050<tab>Psssh psshhh... Pour pêcher plein de poissons, il faut penser... Feltsmox va réfléchir beaucoup beaucoup<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_000<tab>Would you do me a favor, adventurer? Don't worry, it's naught but a simple delivery. I'm just too busy to handle all my orders on my own.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_000<tab>Ah, c'est toi. J'aimerais te confier une nouvelle tâche, une simple livraison. J'ai accepté ce travail, mais je ne vais pas avoir le temps de m'en charger moi-même.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_001<tab>Take this bag of squigglywogs to Feltsmox. You'll most likely find her fishin' out at the Thaliak River. And don't let her worm her way out of payin'─I'm not runnin' a charity here!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_001<tab>Il s'agit d'apporter <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E8B1E0202 /var> à une Gobeline du nom de Feltsmox, qui pêche au bord de la rivière Thaliak. Elle te remettra le paiement.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_010<tab>Feltsmox'll be down at the Thaliak River, fishin' as usual. Take them squigglywogs down to her─and make sure she pays for 'em!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_010<tab>Apporte <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E8B1E0202 /var> à Feltsmox, une Gobeline qui pêche au bord de la rivière Thaliak. Elle te remettra le paiement.

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_020<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
This time, Feltsmox order top-quality fishingbait! Fish will not be able to resist squirming, wriggling squigglywogs. But Feltsmox waits and waits and order of squigglywogs does not arrive...
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_020<tab>Psssh psssh... Feltsmox a commandé un très, très bon hameçon... Mais il n'est pas encore arrivé, pas encore...

source:
TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_021<tab>Pshhh... Shkohhh...
You have them! Feltsmox's squigglywogs! Feltsmox shall catch great many fish.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_021<tab>Pssh pssh... Voilà enfin l'hameçon idéal<var 1D /var>! Avec ça, Feltsmox va pouvoir rattraper le temps perdu, c'est certain<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_022<tab>Thank you for delivering. Please take jinglyshine as payment. Take back to Midnight Dew.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_022<tab>Merci à l'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> pour la livraison<var 1D /var>! Voici le paiement, l'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> doit le donner à Midnight Dew<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_030<tab>Feltsmox already pay! Gave good jinglyshine. Take jinglyshine to Midnight Dew.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_FELTSMOX_000_030<tab>Merci à l'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> pour la livraison<var 1D /var>! Le paiement est à donner à Midnight Dew.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_040<tab>Seems like you didn't have any trouble findin' Feltsmox. You made sure to collect payment, right?
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_040<tab>Feltsmox a dû te donner le paiement pour la livraison de sa commande...

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_041<tab>Thank you. I've no idea when I would've found time to deliver that on my own. Fishin's so popular with these gobbies, them squigglywogs sell as fast as I can get my hands on 'em!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_041<tab>Ah, merci<var 1D /var>! Tu sais, il y a beaucoup de Gobelins qui aiment la pêche, comme Feltsmox.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_042<tab>The goblins here at Idyllshire plan to settle down here together with us, but I think a lot of 'em are wanderers at heart.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_042<tab>Les Gobelins d'Idyllée comptent s'installer ici et s'investir dans la vie du nouveau hameau, mais à l'origine, leur peuple est nomade.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_043<tab>I think Feltsmox's a wanderer. She might stay a while, but I figure one day her wanderlust'll get the better of her, and then she'll leave this place behind.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ813_01943_MIDNIGHTDEW_000_043<tab>J'ai bien l'impression que Feltsmox ne tient pas tellement en place. Je ne serais pas étonnée qu'un jour, elle nous quitte pour reprendre la vie du voyage...
